## üßæ Quick Recap

| Component | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| QUIC | Modern transport protocol |
| HTTP/3 | HTTP over QUIC |
| UDP | Underlying transport |
| Streams | Independent data flows |
| Connection ID | Survives IP changes |

